  "texts": [
    "A previously developed HfSiO x -based SRM was integrated into a 1 kb CA (32 × 32).",
    "Figure 1a shows the scanning electron microscopy images of the CA.",
    "The CA was constructed using a straightforward structure in which the patterned bottom (BE) and top (TE) electrode layers were connected perpendicularly via a crosspoint and individual SRMs were formed at each junction.",
    "The line width for each line comprising the top and bottom electrodes is set at 2 µm, resulting in an effective junction area of 4 µm².",
    "The fabrication details of the CA devices are described in the Methods section."
  ],
